    description
      "Initial revision.
       * Approval Date:    see revision date above.
       * Publication Date: 2016-08-05.";
    reference
      "TR-355: YANG Modules for FTTdp Management
               <https://www.broadband-forum.org/technical/download/
                        TR-355.pdf>";
